[Thu, 28 Nov 2024 23:49:10 GMT] {"user":"rogue","text":"yeah, radio dramas have been around for ages, but i think what mikko's getting at is something more cinematic, like a blockbuster movie but just for your ears. that's a cool idea, but it's not entirely new either. there are already some audio dramas that are pretty immersive, like welcome to night vale or the black tapes. still, i think there's room for more experimentation and innovation in this space.","action":"reply","inReplyTo":"28b72683-3a86-0282-a83e-cb6b6a7504dd"}
